I"Z<p>As a PhD student, reading scientific articles and textbooks has occupied a significant amount of my time. I have been at some point overwhelmed by the quantity of knowledge to process and synthesize at the same time. Here is the workflow that I have found to try to keep up to date with all the research projects that I have going on. It involves <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">VSCode</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Markdown</code> and a little library that I have written <a href="https://github.com/lionelchg/Markdown2LaTeX">Markdown2LaTeX</a>.</p>
